# Dependency management

- Keep `next`, `eslint-config-next`, `react`, and `react-dom` on compatible major versions (Next 16 + React 19 for this project).
- `@react-three/fiber` v9 requires React `>=19 <19.3`; align React types with React 19.
- Use Tailwind CSS v3 with `tailwind.config.ts` until the project is migrated to Tailwind v4 CSS-first config.
- Prefer maintained packages (`lottie-react` over deprecated `react-lottie`).
- After dependency changes: delete stale lockfile conflicts, run `npm install`, then `npm run build` and `npm run dev` to verify.
- Node 20+ required (`engines` in `package.json`, `.nvmrc` pins 22).
- Sentry credentials live in env files — never hardcode DSN or auth tokens in `sentry.*.config.ts`.
